signature.instructions: Analyze the provided images of the Energy Performance Certificate (EPC). Your task is to identify the precise date on which the certificate's validity expires. Extract this date and present it strictly in the YYYY-MM-DD format.

fields.description:
The context of the energy performance certificate (EPC).
        This includes the property address, the energy performance rating, and any other relevant information.

Extract the date until which the energy performance certificate (EPC) is valid.
        Format: YYYY-MM-DD
